reviewText: Excellent gift! I purchased for a friend missing her country & she loves it! I received timely and packaged well. Thanks!

This purchase was well worth it.  The energy and strength put into this work is worth seeing It over and over again.  Angelique has inspiring guest and the music is so uplifting.  The DVD has excellent quality and I would purchase another piece that is produced by her and this group.
Angelique you are the best. An absolute pocket rocket. If you get the chance to see her live, you then love her music more.

I really like this DVD. My only complaint is that it's way too short (an hour maybe?). It's like you get revved up & then it's quickly over. Outstanding performances - by Ms. Kidjo herself of course, Branford Marsalis, Dianne Reeves & Josh Groban. The Fela dancers added a nice touch as did the band (Christian McBride on bass).
